text: This bus stop is mapped at a wrong location. If you map using a bus route and follow the location of this bus stop on Google Map, you will miss your stop and be dropped off in the middle of no where. Alight when you see the Springleaf station that is shown as an earlier stop on the bus route.

This is the new location of this bus-top.
Previously it was located the other side of the junction actually after Springleaf road.
But moved to before Sringleaf road because it is convenient to commuters to board in just after exit from Springleaf MRT exit 2.
